{"tid":1316152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民意點會咁容易被逆轉","createTime":"2019-07-14T15:33:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T18:25:47.000Z","uid":254022,"like":372,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"087799f732c2b7944c315b803a207a8f39d8c4a8","tid":1316152,"uid":254022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:33:00.000Z","msg":"個人睇法<br />\n可能有人認為示威者好暴力，好反感<br />\n但其實有腦都識諗啦<br />\n班黑警濫用暴力、行動唔跟規矩、冒警問題嚴重<br />\n係一個咁唔平等既情況下<br />\n手無寸鐵既市民永遠都比暴政暴權逼迫<br />\n除非有人走去打柒黑警親人，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>否則民意係絕對唔會輕易被逆轉</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以，<br />\n唔該唔好再指責同路人，諗下點解佢地肯上前線<br />\n同埋，成立獨立調查委員會"},{"pid":"1f221fc58fd8f13cf01476a8b01974ac679ff861","tid":1316152,"uid":254022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:33:13.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"92264eddabee210b7b42fa888e38c177e1e877f8","tid":1316152,"uid":254022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:33:29.000Z","msg":"推到有人睇到"},{"pid":"c64b8f36414fbc0e1c7cda703c181c0ee14f8165","tid":1316152,"uid":15808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:33:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8a05bedbd978f1cc42d6d97993142cfa59e74a58","tid":1316152,"uid":108337,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:34:00.000Z","msg":"不切割 冷處理 無條件支持同路人"},{"pid":"05519c6c7b759cac54ea93d2cd27ae309b7fc8c3","tid":1316152,"uid":78429,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:36:09.000Z","msg":"老老實實，就算有人走去打柒黑警親人<br />\n我都唔會有半點動搖"},{"pid":"31f0aef6584038db9100e757f8b788c7f1a0ea43","tid":1316152,"uid":160176,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:36:17.000Z","msg":"這一個月以來，錦多次示威者圍住黑警，都未曾打過一隻狗<br />\n唔係黑警今日又要人散，又要封鎖所有交通工具<br />\n迫示威者埋牆角，示威者需要反擊？<br />\n<br />\n何況個Ｄ拎盾、拎頭盔既撚樣連委任證都無<br />\n點Ｑ知佢地係唔係冒警"},{"pid":"ab8794db3a74564ee4a34bdf0fb0d0c312180dfe","tid":1316152,"uid":254022,"like":0,"dislike":0,